WEBVTT

00:00:15.437 --> 00:00:18.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Did you read
that long ago,

00:00:18.312 --> 00:00:22.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Before the moon
and stars were in the sky,

00:00:22.812 --> 00:00:27.687 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God created his Son?

00:00:27.687 --> 00:00:31.145 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jesus came
to live on earth

00:00:31.145 --> 00:00:35.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Where he healed the sick
and showed what he will do

00:00:35.437 --> 00:00:40.812 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
In the new world to come.

00:00:40.812 --> 00:00:47.187 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
His life he sacrificed
for ev’ryone.

00:00:47.187 --> 00:00:53.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Faithful and True”
—ever loyal from the heart,

00:00:53.770 --> 00:00:59.520 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Faithful in ev’ry way,

00:00:59.520 --> 00:01:06.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As “King of kings,”
he’s ev’rything that a king should be,

00:01:06.770 --> 00:01:16.770 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Bringing us peace
for eternity.

00:01:24.979 --> 00:01:28.854 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now he wears
a golden crown,

00:01:28.854 --> 00:01:33.312 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And he’s soon to rule
an earthly paradise,

00:01:33.312 --> 00:01:38.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Blessing all that we do.

00:01:38.062 --> 00:01:44.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ll see the Bible’s
promises come true.

00:01:44.895 --> 00:01:51.354 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Faithful and True”
—ever loyal from the heart,

00:01:51.354 --> 00:01:57.437 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Faithful in ev’rything.

00:01:57.437 --> 00:02:04.395 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
If we obey, he’ll guide the way
so that we may be

00:02:04.395 --> 00:02:15.604 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Faithful and true for eternity.

